===Noun===
{{en-noun|head=[[line]] [[of]] [[credit]]|lines of credit}}

# {{context|finance|banking|lang=en}} A [[financial]] [[agreement]] under which a [[bank]] or other [[lender]] agrees to provide a [[client]] with [[loan]]s of [[money]] up to an approved [[limit]] during a predefined [[period]]. The client may borrow the entire credit amount all at once or in portions during the specified period.
# {{context|finance|banking|lang=en}} The [[maximum]] [[borrowable]] [[amount]] specified in such an agreement.

